01:04:47,717 --> 01:04:49,176
We will now end the broadcasting

818
01:04:49,260 --> 01:04:51,762
for the inauguration of
the 21st president of Korea.

819
01:04:52,680 --> 01:04:54,473
Thank you, everyone, for watching.

820
